dct_description_sm: From: Galle, Philippe, Epitome du theatre du monde, Antwerp, Officina Plantiniana, 1598. p. 112.
Miniature representation of Ortelius' Palestine after Stella Tilemannus.
French text on verso but related to Asia Minor.
